      "title": "🔍 Core Concept",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "**Upload your character** and apply a pose with **WAN Animate.**\n\n## How It Works\n\n1. **Upload a image**\n2. **Upload a pose reference video**\n3. The system:\n   - Generates a pose estimation **control video**\n   - Uses the pose control video for guiding the diffusion with WAN Animate\n\n## Tips\n\n- Works best if poses and characters are fully in frame\n\nThat's it.  \nCharacter Pose -> Character"
      ],
      "color": "#222",
      "bgcolor": "#000"
    }
